No relationship to the moderator Corvus...


06 Mar 2020 13:34






Alright, Series 6 is live and you just know I needed to get in at least one more of those XX60 spots before we move on to Series 7. It has been a while since I have written anything for Anderson Robotics or Those Twisted Pines, so this is a bit of a return to basics for me, with a largely character driven SCP. Additionally, I felt it was time to start exploring other asspects of the canon away from Vincent Anderson, Edgar Holman, and the Merlo family, so they are distinctly absent here.

Special thanks to DrBleep for holding the original drafts of this over the coals. Wouldn't be nearly as poignant without your input.

Additional thanks to DrMagnus for critique.

Finally, shoutout to my friend Rounderhouse for supplying the image, and allowing its use here/release under CC 3.0 by SA.

Enjoy the article.

JC







